README.md

Awesome

   This is a list of awesome IT quotes. The aim is to collect all relevant
   quotes said over the history of IT.

Contents

     * Alan Kay
     * Alan Turing
     * Albert Einstein
     * Arthur C. Clarke
     * Bill Gates
     * Bjarne Stroustrup
     * Don DeLillo
     * Don Norman
     * Douglas Adams
     * Edsger Dijkstra
     * Edward V. Berard
     * Elbert Hubbard
     * Elon Musk
     * Grace Hopper
     * Harold Abelson
     * Jeff Pesis
     * John Cleese
     * Kathy Sierra
     * Keith Bostic
     * Ken Thompson
     * Larry Wall
     * Linus Torvalds
     * Mark Minasi
     * Martin Fowler
     * Martin Golding
     * Omar Bradley
     * Pablo Picasso
     * Peter Deutsch
     * Richard Stallman
     * Rick Cook
     * Steve Jobs
     * Steve McConnell
     * Sydney Harris
     * Tony Hoare
     * Vidiu Platon

